quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Phir jab yeh Faristaade Lut ke haan pahunchey
  15,62,To usne kaha “aap log ajnabi maloom hotey hain”
  15,63,"Unhon ne jawab diya “nahin, balke hum wahi cheez lekar aaye hain jiske aane mein yeh log shakk kar rahey thay"
  15,64,Hum tumse sach kehte hain ke hum haqq ke saath tumhare paas aaye hain
  15,65,"Lihaza ab tum kuch raat rahey apne ghar walon ko lekar nikal jao aur khud unke peechey peechey chalo, tum mein se koi palat kar na dekhe bas seedhey chale jao jidhar jaane ka tumhein hukum diya jaa raha hai”"
  15,66,Aur usey humne apna yeh faisla pahuncha diya ke subah hotey hotey in logon ki jadd (roots) kaat di jayegi
  15,67,Itne mein shehar ke log khushi ke maarey betab hokar Lut ke ghar chadh aaye
  15,68,"Lut ne kaha “bhaiyon, yeh mere mehmaan hain, meri fazihat (dishonour) na karo"
  15,69,"Allah se daro, mujhey ruswa na karo”"
  15,70,Woh boley “kya hum baaraha tumhein mana nahin kar chuke hain ke duniya bhar ke thekedar na bano?”
  15,71,Lut ne aajiz hokar kaha “agar tumhein kuch karna hi hai to yeh meri betiyan maujood hain”
  15,72,"Teri jaan ki kasam aey Nabi, us waqt unpar ek nasha sa chadha hua tha jismein woh aape se bahar huye jatey thay"
  15,73,Aakhir e kaar pow phathte hi unko ek zabardast dhamake ne aa liya (severe blast overtook them at dawn)
  15,74,Aur humne us basti ko talpat karke rakh diya aur unpar paki (baked) hui mitti ke pattharon ki baarish barsa di
  15,75,Is waqiye mein badi nishaniyan hain un logon ke liye jo saahib-e-firasat hain
  15,76,Aur woh ilaqa (jahan yeh waqiya pesh aaya tha) guzar gaah e aam (high way) par waqeh hai
  15,77,Usmein samaan e ibrat hai un logon ke liye jo sahib e iman hain
  15,78,Aur Aikah waley zalim thay
  15,79,"To dekhlo ke humne unsey bhi inteqam liya, aur in dono qaumon ke ujade huey ilaqe khuley raaste par waqeh hain"